data.description: Hard to find home on acreage in Hamer, Idaho.  This beautiful home is all set up for self sufficiency - it has grapes, raspberries, strawberries, various fruit trees, garden area with pumpkin patch, herbs, flowers, a greenhouse, and chicken coop.  The property has more land that you could build corrals on or anything else you wanted.  There is a Siberian snow pea hedge for privacy and snow/wind block, concrete poured underneath to keep predators out.  There are garden sheds, double garage with storage on both sides, a pump house, beautiful landscaping with mature trees, this is truly a park like setting - the views are amazing as it borders farmland.  Inside you will find windows letting in ample light, large kitchen, cozy fireplaces, large bedrooms and plenty of spaces for storage.  There is a beautiful deck to relax on while watching wildlife and gaze at the gardens!  Seller is also including a home security system as well. The property is being sold as-is.  Please call Tiffany at 208-317-4563 to schedule your showing today!
